snippet.title: Cat Quest 3 - Official Customization Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Play as a seafaring, adventurous cat in Cat Quest 3. Get an all-new look at gameplay here!

Cat Quest 3 is coming to PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch, and PC on August 8th, 2024.
